timeline.bodyText:
This isn't quite right - the Optional returned by forkChoiceStrategy.blockSlot(parentRoot) may be empty (which would indicate we're importing a block from an invalid fork).
We'll want:
Bytes32 parentRoot = root;
    Optional<UnsignedLong> blockSlot = forkChoiceStrategy.blockSlot(parentRoot);
    while (blockSlot.isPresent() && blockSlot.get().compareTo(slot) > 0) {
      parentRoot = forkChoiceStrategy.blockParentRoot(parentRoot).orElseThrow();
      blockSlot = forkChoiceStrategy.blockSlot(parentRoot);
    }
    return blockSlot.isPresent() ? Optional.of(parentRoot) : Optional.empty();

